    Revert stuff converted to FD_PREPARE that does not exist in 6.18
    
    Reverts https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/stable/linux.git/commit/arch/powerpc/platforms/pseries?h=linux-6.18.y&id=09c15bbbed533903e600660ea09098b3b0524f48
